m zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_6106122\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_6106122\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 19, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104exc1707815854341.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/exc1707815854341.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/exc1707815854341.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qjv1665702556414\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Expressions\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"qjv1665702556414__expressions_48637\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">An expression is a ProcScript statement that, after execution, resolves to a value. An expression cannot be executed by itself; it is always used as part of an assignment, condition, or argument, or in a string substitution.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qjv1665702556414__p_d14546e1_d14547e1_d14548e1\">In Uniface, every expression has a string representation. As a consequence, an expression can always be assigned to or substituted in a string. Uniface performs implicit data type conversion if the expression is of a data type other then String.</p>\n<div class=\"note caution note_caution\" id=\"qjv1665702556414__note_w2740ab1b5b5_w2741ab1b5_w2742ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">CAUTION:</span> When testing conditions, you\n         should not rely on implicit type conversion to use strings as if they were Booleans. You\n         should always explicitly state what you are testing for. For example, use <code class=\"ph codeph\">if (var1\n            = \"true\")</code>, not <code class=\"ph codeph\">if (var1)</code>.</div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qjv1665702556414__section_czr_jgp_k1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1115613e65\">Example: Expressions in Conditions, Assignments, and Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qjv1665702556414__p_d14552e1_d14553e1_d14554e1\">The following ProcScript examples show how expressions\n            can be used:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"qjv1665702556414__ul_pyc_mgp_k1c\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qjv1665702556414__li_d7061e1_d7062e1_d7063e1\">In an assignment:\n               <div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"qjv1665702556414__pre_qyc_mgp_k1c\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">myVar = \"My expression\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qjv1665702556414__li_d7064e1_d7065e1_d7066e1\">In a condition:\n               <div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"qjv1665702556414__pre_ryc_mgp_k1c\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">if (myVar = \"My expression\") var1 = var2\nif ($1 = \"My expression\") $2 = $1</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qjv1665702556414__li_d7067e1_d7068e1_d7069e1\">As an argument of a ProcScript Statement:\n               <div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"qjv1665702556414__pre_syc_mgp_k1c\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">putmess \"My expression\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qjv1665702556414__li_d7070e1_d7071e1_d7072e1\">As an argument of a ProcScript Function:\n               <div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"qjv1665702556414__pre_tyc_mgp_k1c\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$1 = $lowercase(\"My expression\")</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qjv1665702556414__li_d7073e1_d7074e1_d7075e1\">ProcScript Function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$time</span> used as\n               an expression in an assignment:\n               <div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"qjv1665702556414__pre_uyc_mgp_k1c\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$1 = $time</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qjv1665702556414__li_d7076e1_d7077e1_d7078e1\">ProcScript Function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$time</span> used as\n               an expression in string substitution:\n               <div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"qjv1665702556414__pre_vyc_mgp_k1c\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">putmess \"The current time is %%$time%%%\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kmc1665702782290.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$expression</a><p>Return the result of evaluating a nonconditional expression.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jbm1707818341035.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Operators</a><p>Operators perform arithmetic, relational, logical, string manipulation, struct member de-reference, operation de-reference, and field indirection operations in ProcScript instructions.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6106122\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6106122\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Expressions Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 19, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Expressions An expression is a ProcScript statement that, after execution, resolves to a value. An expression cannot be executed by itself; it is always used as part of an assignment, condition, or argument, or in a string substitution. In Uniface, every expression has a string representation. As a consequence, an expression can always be assigned to or substituted in a string. Uniface performs implicit data type conversion if the expression is of a data type other then String. CAUTION: When testing conditions, you should not rely on implicit type conversion to use strings as if they were Booleans. You should always explicitly state what you are testing for. For example, use if (var1 = \"true\") , not if (var1) . Example: Expressions in Conditions, Assignments, and Arguments The following ProcScript examples show how expressions can be used: In an assignment: myVar = \"My expression\" Copy In a condition: if (myVar = \"My expression\") var1 = var2 if ($1 = \"My expression\") $2 = $1 Copy As an argument of a ProcScript Statement: putmess \"My expression\" Copy As an argument of a ProcScript Function: $1 = $lowercase(\"My expression\") Copy ProcScript Function $time used as an expression in an assignment: $1 = $time Copy ProcScript Function $time used as an expression in string substitution: putmess \"The current time is %%$time%%%\" Copy Related Links $expression Return the result of evaluating a nonconditional expression. Operators Operators perform arithmetic, relational, logical, string manipulation, struct member de-reference, operation de-reference, and field indirection operations in ProcScript instructions. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}